baj

Netvrk Opdel alle p titel, akt og scene. Vi vil gerne n frem til en grafisk fremstilling af netvrk.

Read one play and all plays into R

Some of the following is designed for finding characteristics for one play. Some of the following is designed for finding characteristics across all plays. Load the JSONL data format

```r
library(tidyverse)
library(ndjson)
library(here)
library(fs)
library(tidytext)

barselstuen_raw <- ndjson::stream_in(here(\test-data/Barselstuen_mod.jsonl\)) %>% tibble()
read_plays_jsonl (here(\test-data\)) ->allplays

##Find navne p alle karakterer med replikker.
Tl alle navngivne karakterer med replikker.

Vi kan ogs lave et skema med speakers opdelt p akt og scene...

```r
all_speakers_with_plays <- allplays %>% 
  count(speaker, docTitle, year) %>%
  group_by(speaker) %>%
  summarise(plays = toString(unique(docTitle)), count = sum(n))
all_speakers_with_plays

write.csv(all_speakers_with_plays, file = here("csv/allspeakers uden navnevarianter med stykker.csv"))
